{
  "stem": "23626.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But then when Adam was telling me that I am the only one to help, and in case they were going to kill us all, they will have enough arms to fight back.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And there were large pipes going out of the camp that some of us could, could run through and also deliver some of the arms.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And since that book came out, one of my friend told me that there is a book and there is a write-up about me, I do speak about it.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because it's written in Polish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Supposedly, they say it's also in Hebrew, in Israel.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I didn't see it, but I have the book.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And it says that the servant of Amon Goeth took big chances by taking out documents from Goeth's drawers in his room and also made copies of passes that helped the underground group.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Unfortunately, the [SIGHS] Ukrainian had denounced Adam Sztap to Goeth.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "One day I was in the yard when Goeth came up on his white horse and stopped in front of the gate.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, Susanna, where is Adam?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I looked up at him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, how does he know that I know Adam?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You see, there were some people that were denouncing things to him, unfortunately.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I looked at him with such surprise.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He went off on his horse.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "A couple of minutes later, I heard two shots.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] My girlfriend told me-- she was there-- they brought Adam down.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He gave order to look for him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He asked him, where do you keep your arms?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And Adam said, I don't have any arms.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He pulled out the gun.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Well, we'll continue on the next tape.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
